{{vgname|足球经理2017|en=Football Manager 2017}}是{{link-en|Sports Interactive|Sports Interactive}}开发，[[世嘉|世嘉]]发行的足球题材[[模拟经营游戏|模拟经营游戏]]，2016年11月4日推出正式版。

==官方汉化==
游戏的系列总监{{le|迈尔斯·雅各布森|Miles Jacobson}}曾发推，说中文区卖出两万套就出[[中文化#官方中文化|官方中文版]]，结果后来又不认账，这使得游戏在[[Steam|Steam]]上获得了中文区玩家的差评，并导致游戏的差评率被刷破70%。<ref>{{cite web|title=《足球经理2017》无中文获70%差评 称收死亡威胁|url=http://games.sina.com.cn/t/n/2016-11-02/fxxfysn8625019.shtml|website=games.sina.com.cn|publisher=SINA Corporation|accessdate=2016-11-03|date=2016-11-02|archive-date=2016-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161103142206/http://games.sina.com.cn/t/n/2016-11-02/fxxfysn8625019.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>最后发行商世嘉宣布推出繁体中文版，<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://steamcommunity.com/app/482730/discussions/0/312265473879145495/ |title = Chinese localisation. |author = SEGA DEV |date = 2016-10-29 |publisher =  |language = en |accessdate = 2017-02-12 |archive-date = 2017-02-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170212165131/http://steamcommunity.com/app/482730/discussions/0/312265473879145495/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>2017年4月3日优先推出官方简体中文版。<ref>{{cite web|title=简体中文版现已面世|url=http://steamcommunity.com/games/482730/announcements/detail/486793695390157485|accessdate=2017-04-04|date=2017-04-03|archive-date=2017-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170404131201/http://steamcommunity.com/games/482730/announcements/detail/486793695390157485|dead-url=no}}</ref>

